# Task 3 – Stakeholder Mapping

## Project
Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description
This task identifies the stakeholders involved in the Smart Library Request Workflow and defines their roles, responsibilities, expectations, and interactions with the system.

## Stakeholders
- Students
- Librarians
- System Administrators
- Management / Faculty
- IT Support Team

## Objectives
- Define stakeholder roles
- Improve communication
- Clarify responsibilities
- Support effective collaboration
- Ensure successful project implementation

## Expected Outcome
A clear stakeholder map that helps in planning, communication, system development, and long-term maintenance.

## Technologies
- ServiceNow
- Workflow Management
- Access Control Lists (ACL)
- Reporting

## Status
Completed
